news.title: Kaisa Group liquidation petition adjourned by Hong Kong court
news.para: The Shenzhen-based developer has been working to restructure its offshore debt for two years after defaulting on $12 billion in offshore debt in late 2021.

news.title: Birla Estates acquires 16.5 acres land in Pune
news.para: The land parcel has a development potential of approximately 32 lakh sq ft and an estimated revenue potential of Rs 2,500 crore.

news.title: Only 195 projects set up grievance redressal cell despite MahaRERA directive
news.para: The regulator has undertaken a review of the same and is now planning to initiate action against the developers that are not in compliance with the directive issued in August 2023 with an objective of resolving homebuyers’ grievances.
